<view class='index'>
    <view class='index-top'>
        <image class='index-logo' src='/images/icon_component.png'></image>
        <view class='index-desc'>
            以下将展示小程序官方组件能力，组件样式仅供参考，开发者可根据自身需求自定义组件样式，具体属性参数详见<navigator class="weui-agree__link" url='www.baidu.com'>百度搜索</navigator>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class='index-bd'>
        <block 
            wx:for="{{ list }}" 
            wx:for-item="item" 
            wx:for-index="index"
            wx:key="{{ index }}">
            <view 
                id='{{ item.id }}' 
                class='list-item  {{item.open ? "list-item-bd-show" : ""}}'
                bindtap="showToggle">
                <view class='list-item-hd'>
                    <view class='list-item-text'>{{ item.name }}</view>
                    <image class='list-item-img' src='/images/{{ item.id }}.png'></image>
                </view>
                <view class='list-item-bd'>
                    <view 
                        class='list-item-evel' 
                        wx:for="{{ item.pages }}" 
                        wx:for-item="evel" 
                        wx:for-index="idx"
                        wx:key="{{ idx }}">
                        <navigator class='list-link'>
                            <view class='list-item-evel-text'>{{ evel }}</view>
                            <icon class="iconfont icon-right"></icon>
                        </navigator>
                    </view>
                </view>
            </view>
        </block>
    </view>
</view>
